// Standalone workspace for the Wails desktop app. It shadows the monorepo's
// root go.work so `go`/`wails` invoked inside app/desktop build this module in
// isolation: the desktop shares no code with the Go runtime modules and pulls
// Wails/CGO deps the backend workspace must not absorb. Without this file, a
// build here walks up to ../../go.work — which does not list this module — and
// fails with "directory ... does not contain modules listed in go.work".
go 1.24.4

use .
